15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 1308.3, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 1308.3. Any active employee eligible to participate or
19 who is a participant may opt out of the state's basic plan as
20 outlined in Sections 1370 and 1371 of this title, or may opt out of
21 the health and dental basic plan options only, and retain the life
22 and disability plan benefits, provided that the participant is
23 currently covered by a separate group health insurance plan or will
24 be covered by a separate group health insurance plan at or before
